text: Finsterwalde is a town in Elbe-Elster in Brandenburg, Germany. In 2021, 15,748 people lived there. "We are the singers from Finsterwalde", a hit from the late 19th century. == Geography == Finsterwalde is in the Lower Lusatia region. It is south of Berlin and north of Dresden. == History == Finsterwalde was first mentioned in 1282 as Vynsterwalde. == References == == Other websites == *
